{"lemma":"عُزَّلُ","slug":"عُزَّلُ","root":"ع.ز.ل","root_slug":"ع-ز-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ز-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"عُزَّلُ","root":"عزل","pos":"V","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":0},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["","n28983","n28984","n28985","n28986"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8F%D8%B2%D9%8E%D9%91%D9%84%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n28983","headword_ar":"عَزْلٌ","root":"Ezl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What is brought to the treasury of the state in advance, not weighed, nor picked so as to have the bad put forth from it, to the time of the falling-due of the instalment:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA:) [for the second of the last three words of the explanation, which are correctly"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilaY maHil~i Aln~ajomi","text_ar":"اـِلَى مَحِلِّ النَّجْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", the O has"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mHali","text_ar":"محَلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; the CK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHal~i","text_ar":"مَحَلِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and my MS. copy of the K,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mHl","text_ar":"محل"},{"kind":"text","text":", without any vowel-sign and without the sheddeh:] from Ibn-'Abbád; (O;) and thus in the L. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["O","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n28984","headword_ar":"عُزْلٌ","root":"Ezl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n28985","headword_ar":"عَزَلٌ","root":"Ezl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eazila","text_ar":"عَزِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition, of not having with one any weapon;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuzolN","text_ar":"عُزْلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K, TA: [the latter, by reason of an ambiguity in the K, misunderstood by Freytag as syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EizaAlN","text_ar":"عِزَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense in which this is expl. in the CK:]) they are two dial. vars., like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$agalN","text_ar":"شَغَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ugolN","text_ar":"شُغْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baxalN","text_ar":"بَخَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buxolN","text_ar":"بُخْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A deficiency in one of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaroqafataAni","text_ar":"حَرْقَفَتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the crest of one of the two hip-bones"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (IAar, O, K.) ―         -b4-  And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hinder part"},{"kind":"text","text":"of an ass: so in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiqoraEo Eazala HimaArika","text_ar":"اِقْرَعْ عَزَلَ حِمَارِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Strike thou the binder part of thy ass"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (O, K:) said to the driver of the ass. (O.)"}],"source_refs":["O","K"]},{"entry_id":"n28986","headword_ar":"عُزُلٌ","root":"Ezl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEozalu","text_ar":"اَعْزَلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}